    <exercise number="3"><statement>
            <p>On October 31, Betty and Paul fill their <m>250</m>-gallon oil tank for their heater. Beginning in November, they use an average of <m>15</m> gallons of oil per week. Complete the table of values for the amount of oil, <m>A</m>, left in the tank after <m>w</m> weeks.</p>
